{"tid":716098,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呃求職者資料借百萬　6人被捕","createTime":"2018-06-25T03:55:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-25T05:45:40.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8d61b0c3aeba8355f13bcc0fc0fa6d29459f8b3f","tid":716098,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T03:55:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180625/20430768\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180625%2F20430768&d=m%2FcvgakCNBeKT3vUml5W9UjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=57570d78\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180625%2F20430768&h=0831f62c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180625/20430768</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月25日 <br />\n<br />\n呃求職者資料借百萬　6人被捕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180625/large/25la3p5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180625%2Flarge%2F25la3p5.jpg&h=85f03135&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■其中一名疑犯昨被探員蒙頭押走調查。劉柏麟攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方調查發現，有騙徒在網上招聘兼職推廣員，並以高時薪利誘求職者應聘，然後盜取求職者個人資料借貸及申領信用卡，先後有16名女子中招，部份為學生，涉及金額逾100萬元。警方先後拘捕6名男女，並起回部份事主身份證及假文件。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以年輕女性為目標<br />\n<br />\n涉串謀詐騙被捕的4男2女（16至34歲）包括集團骨幹成員，其中一名25歲男子被落案控以一項串謀欺詐罪，今日解上西九龍裁判法院應訊，一人仍被扣查，其餘4人獲准保釋候查。<br />\n<br />\n16名女事主由19至28歲，警方稱該集團以年輕女性為目標，已運作兩個多月，騙徒盜取事主資料後即會製作住址及收入證明等文件，然後申請借貸，其中最大一宗借貸金額達10萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警方今年4月接獲受害人報案，指在facebook上見到招聘兼職推廣員的廣告，時薪由150至200元，主要為有關公司派發小禮物或紀念品，她們不虞有詐應聘，按對方要求在西九龍兩個大型商場會面。<br />\n<br />\n其間騙徒要求事主提供身份證、住址證明及提款卡等個人資料以安排工作，其後騙徒藉詞替事主影印文件盜走正本及逃去，其中6人被盜走提款卡，事主報警。旺角警方調查後，於本月12日至昨日拘捕6人。<br />\n<br />\n■記者劉柏麟  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n「密語」騙局受害人200萬變$800<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n今起招股　銀行券商推孖展優惠　 10個專家8個睇淡　 「小米博唔過」"},{"pid":"6a6da64e788b70c665b3bc73c28925c934abc4b9","tid":716098,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T04:16:34.000Z","msg":"先後有16名女子中招<br />\n<br />\n全部港女中招???<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26ca69e1407382a13ce8151e6845846e27cc32ba","tid":716098,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T04:18:14.000Z","msg":"其實點樣借到, 無身份證比人影印都借到錢? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e1f9999ff83cb76cd80e603d984c106cee33416","tid":716098,"uid":82028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T05:45:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180625/20430768\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180625%2F20430768&d=m%2FcvgakCNBeKT3vUml5W9UjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=57570d78\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180625%2F20430768&h=0831f62c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180625/20430768</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180625/large/25la3p5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180625%2Flarge%2F25la3p5.jpg&h=85f03135&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n 詹瑞文拉人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}